**2017年 - BizTalk Server 2016 Feature Pack 1（整合[[Power_BI|Power BI]]； [[Swagger_(software)|Swagger]]與[[REST|REST API]]相容）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://aka.ms/biztalkfp1|title=BizTalk Server 2016 Feature Pack 1| publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]] | work=[[Microsoft_Azure|Azure]] |access-date=2016-04-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/biztalk_server_team_blog/2017/04/26/biztalk-server-2016-feature-pack-1-is-live/|title=BizTalk Server 2016 Feature Pack 1 is live – BizTalk Team Blog|website=blogs.msdn.microsoft.com|access-date=2019-02-06|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426154322/https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/biztalk_server_team_blog/2017/04/26/biztalk-server-2016-feature-pack-1-is-live/}}</ref>
